    dc:description "FIGURES 73–84. Pseudodysderina manu, new species, male (73–80) and female (81–84). 73. Sternum, ventral view. 74. Left palp, prolateral view. 75. Same, ventral view. 76. Same, retrolateral view. 77. Left embolus, prolateral view. 78. Same, ventral view. 79. Same, retrolateral view. 80. Labium and endites, ventral view. 81. Abdomen, ventral view. 82, 83. Female genitalia, ventral view. 84. Same, dorsal view." ;
